\section*{\LARGE Copyright Notice / 版权声明 / 版權宣告}

\textbf{\textsf{General Relativity}} is a graduate textbook and reference on Albert Einstein's general theory of relativity written by the gravitational physicist Robert Wald. This work is used to retype the original work in \textsf{\LaTeX}, please do not use it for any commercial purposes.

In this remake, the pictures of the original work have been redrawn. Due to my limited ability, it is inevitable that some sentences, formulas, and typesetting will occur Error, welcome to give me feedback via email \href{mailto:xiamyphys@gmail.com}{xiamyphys@gmail.com}.

The painting reproduced on the cover of the paperback version of this book is René Magritte's \emph{Les Belles Réalités}, \copyright by ADAGP, Paris, 1984. Picture source \href{https://pinterest.com}{Pinterest}.

